What you need to know:  The men's race will equally be a sight to behold with Gikuni Ndung'u, who is fresh from finishing third in the World Cup Series, in actionThe senior men's 13km race will go down at 9.10am, just after the senior women's 13km at 9amThe junior men and women race will open the proceedings at 8am with the 2km race closing the event at 11.15am